Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這些東西怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,誒  什麼  我沒聽清
